milestones.description: Hadlee has broken the record for most ducks (4) in ODIs for NZ, going past Dayle Hadlee's 3
Jeremy Coney and Martin Crowe's 93-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 70 between Lance Cairns and Jeff Crowe
Warren Lees has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (4) in ODIs for NZ, going past Ken Wadsworth's 3
